{"tid":530079,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 史篤城揾到新領隊","createTime":"2018-01-15T12:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T13:49:23.000Z","uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"127d863767b9a7241bb347efe54335110745eeb4","tid":530079,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T12:16:26.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Lrxid1YbcL63Z1wYTkUQ%2Bh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=c7adc7bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周一出征曼聯前，史篤城宣佈聘用前阿士東維拉領隊林拔執教。<br />\n<br />\n史篤城於周一宣佈林拔（Paul Lambert）已簽約2年半。他在周一英超作客曼聯暫不會領軍，只做觀眾，到周二才於記者會首次以史篤城主帥身份會見傳媒；到周六英超主場鬥哈特斯菲爾德，就是其在新東家的首戰。<br />\n<br />\n主席高亞迪斯表示：「林拔對我們球隊的認識，令我印象十分深刻，而且他已有明確的計劃去改善成績。我們希望任命一名有英超經驗或認為英格蘭足球的人，所以很期待跟他合作，亦會全力支持他達成球會的目標。」<br />\n<br />\n48歲的林拔曾帶領諾域治升上英超，名聲就此而起，到2012年轉教阿士東維拉，可惜因為資金不多而未能踢出成績，執教了2年半就離隊，之後曾入主布力般流浪及狼隊這2支低組別球會。"},{"pid":"4b79381b192995f8a3d7071b87b64e8c043005b7","tid":530079,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"叫高治做算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8460e70499127e87be8a3baf81b9e2387d635a","tid":530079,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b79381b192995f8a3d7071b87b64e8c043005b7","tid":530079,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"叫高治做算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T12:48:07.000Z","msg":"What at..."},{"pid":"42a7fc6b1a9efeabb24be0de1fb41447c83a4c50","tid":530079,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"玩返以前果套高q大棍手榴彈戰術啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3d3b6ea5cb77fd4d8ad68033c65514b3789ca7","tid":530079,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"對波要